Title: The Chinese Restaurant
Plot: Jerry, Elaine and George stop for a quick Chinese dinner before a showing of Plan 9 From Outer Space on the big screen. However, while waiting a really long time to get a table, Jerry sees a woman whose name he can't recall; George needs to use a phone he can't have and Elaine needs food, more than those seated ahead of them.
GuestStars: Larry David, James Hong, David Tress, Judy Kain, Kate Benton, Michael Mitz, Kendall McCarthy
